
@startuml
skinparam linetype=cloud

class Organizer {
  - firstName: String
  - lastName: String
  - email: String
  - postalAddress: String
  - phoneNumber: String
  - password: String
  - isAttending: Boolean
}

class Attendee {
  - firstName: String
  - lastName: String
  - email: String
  - password: String
  - attendanceStatus: String // "will attend", "maybe", "cannot attend"
}

class Event {
  - name: String
  - startDate: DateTime
  - endDate: DateTime
  - occasion: String
  - location: Location
  - organizers: List<Organizer>
  - attendees: List<Attendee>
  - checklist: Checklist
}

class Location {
  - name: String
  - address: String
}

class Checklist {
  - tasks: List<Task>
}

class Task {
  - description: String
  - status: String // "needs to be done", "done", "not applicable"
  - assignedTo: Attendee
}

class EventType {
  - name: String
}

class EventCategory {
  - name: String
  - events: List<Event>
}

class Invitation {
  - sender: Organizer
  - recipient: Attendee
  - event: Event
  - status: String // "pending", "accepted", "declined", "maybe"
}

Organizer "1" -- "0..*" Event : organizes
Event "1" -- "1" Location : has
Event "1" -- "1" EventType : type
Event "1" -- "0..*" Invitation : sends
Invitation "1" -- "1" Attendee : sent to
Event "1" -- "1" Checklist : has
Checklist "1" -- "0..*" Task : contains
Task "0..1" -- "1" Attendee : assigned to
Organizer "1" -- "0..*" Invitation : sends
Attendee "1" -- "0..*" Invitation : receives
@enduml

---

### 📌 Explanation of Classes and Relationships:

- **`Organizer`**: Manages events, can attend or not, has personal details.
- **`Attendee`**: Can receive invitations, respond to them, and take on tasks if assigned.
- **`Event`**: Central entity with start/end times, location, occasion, etc. Has a list of organizers and attendees.
- **`Location`**: Stores the name and address of an event location.
- **`EventType`**: Represents types of events like birthday party, graduation, etc.
- **`Checklist`**: Contains a list of `Task`s for an event.
- **`Task`**: Describes a task that needs to be completed, optionally assigned to an attendee.
- **`Invitation`**: Represents the invitation sent from an organizer to an attendee.

